### ARTICLE VI: BREACH, REMEDIES, AND TERMINATION

6.1 MATERIAL BREACH: The following actions constitute material breach of 
    this License:
    (a) Unauthorized resale, redistribution, or licensing of the Assets;
    (b) Use of automated AI/ML scraping tools to extract or duplicate 
